text:
Hey Daniel! Thanks so much! I hope you're well. Any exciting news you can share with me?

I've finished a breakdown of one of the pro shots I worked on! If you have the time I'd love to hear any feedback you might have: <https://youtu.be/xXTvt_HubHo>

Can I ask more about the text document to include explaining my role? Is there a particular format I should follow and things to include?

Take care!
